      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Meticulously maintained and free of any cosmetic or mechanical imperfections, it offers a driving experience indistinguishable from new. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who demands nothing less than perfection in every detail.",
